  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb \u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db4\u0daf\u0dd2\u0d82\u0da0\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0d87\u0dbb\u0db9\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "National fuel license registration begins",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Minister of Power and Energy Kanchana Wijesekera said this afternoon that the issuance of a 'National Fuel Licence' and vehicle registration will begin today (16) to streamline fuel distribution.",
        "Accordingly, the vehicle owners can register through the fuelpass.gov.lk website, Minister Kanchana Wijesekera further stated."
      ],
